reviewText: This is the first animated DC universe movie I bought on account of I like Harley quinn and after seeing the suicide squad movie trailer I saw this it came off as truly from the arkham series universe and the joker was the best well drawn in this movie than the other ones I seen him in
Was the perfect birthday gift for my wife she loved it and watches over and over
This is a good movie. Action kept us entertained.
